              Flower Boy
            </a>
          </h4>
          <p class="album_description">
            Flower Boy is the fourth studio album by American rapper Tyler, the Creator. The album, which is his second under a major record label, was released on July 21, 2017, by Columbia Records. Although the album's production was handled entirely by Tyler, the Creator himself, it features guest vocals from a range of artists, including Frank Ocean, ASAP Rocky, Anna of the North, Lil Wayne, Kali Uchis, Steve Lacy, Estelle, Jaden Smith and Rex Orange County.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="album">
          <%= image_tag("unknown_pleasures.jpg", class: "album-image") %>
